casebody.data:
MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

94-401. Westside Cellular, Inc. v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, No. 89-563-TP-COI. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio. Upon consideration of the joint application to dismiss,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective July 21, 1994.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
